Dr. '''J. Ronald Eastman''' is a Professor of Geography at [[Clark University]] and the author and chief developer of [[IDRISI]] GIS Software. In 2003, Eastman received the [[Ronald F. Abler]] Distinguished Service Honors from the [[Association of American Geographers]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=AAG|title=Honors|url=http://www.aag.org/honors|publisher=American Association of Geographers|accessdate=8 May 2018}}</ref> Eastman was awarded the [[Distinguished Career Award]] at the 2010 Annual AAG Meeting.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.clarku.edu/faculty/facultybio.cfm?id=61|title=Faculty {{!}} Clark University|website=www.clarku.edu|language=en|access-date=2018-05-08}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://gistbok.ucgis.org/ucgis-awards/ron-eastman|title=Ron Eastman {{!}} GIS&T Body of Knowledge|website=gistbok.ucgis.org|language=en|access-date=2018-05-08}}</ref>

